"type":169,"tag":170,"props":171,"children":173},"element","h2",{"id":172},"twitter",[174],{"type":169,"tag":175,"props":176,"children":180},"a",{"href":177,"rel":178},"https://x.com/budibase?utm_campaign=Onboarding&utm_medium=email&_hsenc=p2ANqtz--6Ynd76E4FehE07-MjjIZWwvuH2B-KMkxdBPT1TJ5Eh4ci9Wy0q_RZYTIRBsGXz_09u4n_C8GiUe9f8mFjiC6Dj9B4sw&_hsmi=66516363&utm_content=66516363&utm_source=hs_automation",[179],"nofollow",[181],{"type":182,"value":183},"text","Twitter",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":186,"children":187},"p",{},[188],{"type":182,"value":189},"2020 年那会儿 Budibase 从 SlackHQ 迁移到 Discord，发布了他的第一条推文，尽管点赞数量只有寥寥三个。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":191,"children":192},{},[193],{"type":169,"tag":194,"props":195,"children":197},"img",{"alt":163,"src":196},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031913704.png",[],{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":199,"children":200},{},[201],{"type":182,"value":202},"推崇 Sarah Drasner 的空盒子概念，即“也许我们可以从一个空盒子开始，这个盒子只包含正在解决的问题的核心用例或问题”，而不是看到周围完整的网站或应用而感到自卑。Budibase 认为它是一个空盒子，为用户抽象了构建 Web 应用的复杂性。PRay 也是如此，并且应当在多用户交互上大有改进。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":204,"children":205},{},[206],{"type":182,"value":207},"Joe Johnston（应该是 budibase 成员）在 2020 年发表了 What is custom software development in 2025，讨论了“定制化软件开发”需求的广阔场景。",{"type":169,"tag":209,"props":210,"children":211},"blockquote",{},[212],{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":213,"children":214},{},[215],{"type":182,"value":216},"定制软件开发是指为特定问题、用户或人群设计、开发、部署、维护和提供软件支持的过程。理解定制软件开发的关键在于认识到正在开发的解决方案是为单一、特定的目的/问题量身定制的——通常无法通过现有的解决方案来解决。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":218,"children":219},{},[220],{"type":182,"value":221},"SaaS 软件（COTS 商业现货软件）单价比定制低，但远没有定制乃至自建来得灵活。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":223,"children":224},{},[225],{"type":182,"value":226},"“when COTS software did not solve the problem for SMEs, tools like Excel and Access were drafted in and a solution glued together”，Excel 作为从业者的信息交换工具，类似 Python、Lua 在游戏引擎中的胶水作用。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":228,"children":229},{},[230],{"type":182,"value":231},"今天正好是 2025 年 1 月，我认为 budibase 对软件开发的认识很有前瞻性。其观点也符合我的两点认识：第一，软件开发应该面向更广阔的 C 端，在知识爆炸并有势形成超级个体的时代，代码技能（实际上是指通过人机界面制定规则并实现需求）是全民必备的技能；第二，新时代的消费包含了新时代的创造，消费时间不仅仅通过娱乐，也可以包含创造性的方式，如同我的世界、乐高等。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":233,"children":234},{},[235],{"type":182,"value":236},"文章引用了 Percolate、Oribi、Monese 三个工具来说明定制软件如何解决问题，但没用过评价不了。实际上这可能只是为了文章的 SEO。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":238,"children":239},{},[240],{"type":182,"value":241},"2020-10-02 发布了一个暗黑风格的界面，是制作内容的暗黑风格，而不是 budibase 的。其本地的暗黑模式是在 2020-11-06 号发布的（已经过了公测前两周），不过这速度也太快了。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":243,"children":244},{},[245],{"type":182,"value":246},"有人发推推荐了一些产品，包括 budibase，剩下一些可能值得观摩的：",{"type":169,"tag":248,"props":249,"children":250},"ul",{},[251,262,272],{"type":169,"tag":252,"props":253,"children":254},"li",{},[255],{"type":169,"tag":175,"props":256,"children":259},{"href":257,"rel":258},"https://x.com/PoryHQ",[179],[260],{"type":182,"value":261},"PoryHQ",{"type":169,"tag":252,"props":263,"children":264},{},[265],{"type":169,"tag":175,"props":266,"children":269},{"href":267,"rel":268},"https://x.com/bildrHQ",[179],[270],{"type":182,"value":271},"bildrHQ",{"type":169,"tag":252,"props":273,"children":274},{},[275],{"type":169,"tag":175,"props":276,"children":279},{"href":277,"rel":278},"https://x.com/draftbit",[179],[280],{"type":182,"value":281},"draftbit",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":283,"children":284},{},[285,287,294],{"type":182,"value":286},"有个 Tag 叫做 ",{"type":169,"tag":288,"props":289,"children":291},"code",{"className":290},[],[292],{"type":182,"value":293},"#100DaysOfNoCode",{"type":182,"value":295},"，看着不错。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":297,"children":298},{},[299],{"type":182,"value":300},"Bubibase 推荐了 Martin McKeveney 的 NoSQL 和 DynamoDB 的演讲。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":302,"children":303},{},[304],{"type":182,"value":305},"展示了一些预制的渐变色（UI 还可以优化）：",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":307,"children":308},{},[309],{"type":169,"tag":194,"props":310,"children":312},{"alt":163,"src":311},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031950748.png",[],{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":314,"children":315},{},[316],{"type":182,"value":317},"2020-10-22 发布了不推荐生产环境使用的公共测试版本。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":319,"children":320},{},[321],{"type":182,"value":322},"在什么是你建 Web App 时最喜欢的工作内容时，没有人投票给“测试”。不过，反向思考，能辅助用户做测试的工具可能也是很有市场的。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":324,"children":325},{},[326],{"type":169,"tag":194,"props":327,"children":329},{"alt":163,"src":328},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031954506.png",[],{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":331,"children":332},{},[333],{"type":182,"value":334},"TechCrunch 的一篇 The No-Code Generation is arriving 文章中，根据“In the distant past, there was a proverbial “digital divide” that bifurcated workers into those who knew how to use computers and those who didn’t.”推演了今后数据分析工程在今后可能作为新的“数字鸿沟”出现以及带来的影响。而这正是过去几年（2017~2020）低代码发力的方向，AirTable 和 Retool 这种年轻的公司分别以 26 亿以及 10 亿美元的估值崛起。文章还提到了“而像 Bildr、Shogun、Bubble、Stacker”等公司，但是我没有用过。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":336,"children":337},{},[338,345],{"type":169,"tag":175,"props":339,"children":342},{"href":340,"rel":341},"https://nocodelist.co/",[179],[343],{"type":182,"value":344},"NocodeList",{"type":182,"value":346},"，收集了 300+ 无代码工具，而他本身就是一个很适合无代码建设的网站。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":348,"children":349},{},[350],{"type":169,"tag":194,"props":351,"children":353},{"alt":163,"src":352},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032006061.png",[],{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":355,"children":356},{},[357],{"type":182,"value":358},"数据看起来还不错，两周的公测信息。公测后两周的数据没有前两周好看。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":360,"children":361},{},[362],{"type":182,"value":363},"🔻 606 downloads\n🤖 619 apps created\n🚀 246 apps deployed",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":365,"children":366},{},[367],{"type":182,"value":368},"在公测第三个月时，bb 积累了 3200+ 用户、2400+ 应用，以及 554 个部署的应用。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":370,"children":371},{},[372],{"type":182,"value":373},"2020-11-09 发布的图表功能，第一版的功能比较简单，但是很有视觉风格：",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":375,"children":376},{},[377],{"type":169,"tag":194,"props":378,"children":380},{"alt":163,"src":379},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032011651.png",[],{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":382,"children":383},{},[384],{"type":182,"value":385},"2020-12-20 称自己是“open organization”，可以在 Github 上看到他们的项目路线图，甚至是参与讨论。这种事情（类似完成度的产品）在国内就算放到 2025 年也很难想象。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":387,"children":388},{},[389],{"type":182,"value":390},"2020-12-09 在 budibase，15 分钟就能创造一个 Winamp 风格的界面。也许包括功能？链接打不开了，无法验证。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":392,"children":393},{},[394],{"type":169,"tag":194,"props":395,"children":397},{"alt":163,"src":396},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032144479.png",[],{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":399,"children":400},{},[401],{"type":182,"value":402},"“将 Star 数量视为开源社区的货币”这一信念让 Joe Johnston 开始 budibase 的 Github 星星之旅。在 11~12 月间，其数量从 83 个增长到了接近 500，在图上来看这就是指数级别的增长！在博客中分享了其做法。时间来到次年 2 月，Star 数量超过 2000，两倍超越了他们的去年的既定目标。",{"type":169,"tag":248,"props":404,"children":405},{},[406,410,415,420],{"type":169,"tag":252,"props":407,"children":408},{},[409],{"type":182,"value":183},{"type":169,"tag":252,"props":411,"children":412},{},[413],{"type":182,"value":414},"邮件引导指向 Github 并告知路线图、代码都在 Github",{"type":169,"tag":252,"props":416,"children":417},{},[418],{"type":182,"value":419},"budibase 制作的项目支持 Github 调用",{"type":169,"tag":252,"props":421,"children":422},{},[423],{"type":182,"value":424},"更新 Readme",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":426,"children":427},{},[428],{"type":182,"value":429},"而他们新的 Readme 也确实很有吸引力（“Build business apps 50x faster”）：",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":431,"children":432},{},[433],{"type":169,"tag":194,"props":434,"children":436},{"alt":163,"src":435},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032149799.png",[],{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":438,"children":439},{},[440],{"type":182,"value":441},"“As companies, we often look outwards for growth, but looking inwards can provide opportunities. Optimizing processes, analyzing data, & equipping staff with the right tools is often an easier win for many companies; this is where low-code platforms will continue to succeed.”，最有意思的配图。包括上文提到的 2025 软件定制需求前瞻一文中的配图，都是相同类型的矢量图，很有意思。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":443,"children":444},{},[445],{"type":169,"tag":194,"props":446,"children":448},{"alt":163,"src":447},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032152157.png",[],{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":450,"children":451},{},[452],{"type":182,"value":453},"2021 年初，关于希望使用哪个平台托管 bb，居然没有 AWS。前两名 Heroku 和 DigitalOcean 几乎占据了 100% 的投票。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":455,"children":456},{},[457],{"type":169,"tag":194,"props":458,"children":460},{"alt":163,"src":459},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032154794.png",[],{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":462,"children":463},{},[464],{"type":182,"value":465},"还有另一个投票也显示了 Twitter 上用户的数据库偏好，第一名居然是 Google Sheets。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":467,"children":468},{},[469],{"type":169,"tag":194,"props":470,"children":472},{"alt":163,"src":471},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032156394.png",[],{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":474,"children":475},{},[476,478,485],{"type":182,"value":477},"推荐了一个如何启动开源项目并扩大其影响力的网站，里面有一系列文章：",{"type":169,"tag":175,"props":479,"children":482},{"href":480,"rel":481},"https://opensource.guide/",[179],[483],{"type":182,"value":484},"Open Source Guides",{"type":182,"value":486},"。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":488,"children":489},{},[490],{"type":182,"value":491},"Tech Nation 的 Rising Stars 3 奖项包含了 bb。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":493,"children":494},{},[495],{"type":182,"value":496},"2021-04-13 招聘 3 名 JavaScript 工程师。基于之前他发过关于 Svelte 的迷因，我猜创始人对 Svelte 依旧比较感兴趣。同月 25 号，bb 赞助了 Svelte Summit。直到次年 1 月，他们才开始招聘产品负责人、JS 工程师、产品教育经历、产品设计和客户成功经理，可见扩张得比较节制。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":498,"children":499},{},[500],{"type":182,"value":501},"那么，下一步是什么？我也想问。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":503,"children":504},{},[505],{"type":169,"tag":194,"props":506,"children":508},{"alt":163,"src":507},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032244873.png",[],{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":510,"children":511},{},[512],{"type":182,"value":513},"百姓网的知识库里面也有很多内部应用，但是年久失修。我管他们叫幽灵应用。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":515,"children":516},{},[517],{"type":169,"tag":194,"props":518,"children":520},{"alt":163,"src":519},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032251644.png",[],{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":522,"children":523},{},[524],{"type":182,"value":525},"2021-10-22 发布了新的响应式拖拽，看起来用户体验很好。PRay 马上跟进。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":527,"children":528},{},[529],{"type":169,"tag":530,"props":531,"children":534},"video",{"src":532,"controls":162,"width":533},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032256999.mp4","100%",[535],{"type":182,"value":536},"Your browser does not support the video tag.",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":538,"children":539},{},[540],{"type":182,"value":541},"不过 bb 的界面很总是看起来很“Notion”。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":543,"children":544},{},[545],{"type":169,"tag":194,"props":546,"children":548},{"alt":163,"src":547},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032308303.png",[],{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":550,"children":551},{},[552],{"type":182,"value":553},"2021-11-16 日，“经过两年的开发，我们激动的宣布正式在 product hunt 上进行官方宣传”。而他们的商业化也确实非常成功。2022-10-03 甚至创办了 5000 刀的低代码马拉松。",{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":555,"children":556},{},[557],{"type":169,"tag":194,"props":558,"children":560},{"alt":163,"src":559},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032310378.png",[],{"type":169,"tag":185,"props":562,"children":563},{},[564],{"type":169,"tag":194,"props":565,"children":567},{"alt":163,"src":566},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/